title: THE TOP TEN COMEDY VIDEOS of the Annus Horribilis 2020 (+ 10 More)  (The Meaning Of Comedy in 2020)
description:
And so as we rapidly cram the Annus Horribilis 2020 in the history books of the 21st Century to be forgotten, because who reads history anymore, there was indeed one bright spot worth mentioning. There were a collection of indiviuals on YouTube (YouTubers?) (Can we call them influencers?) (No, probably not.), who managed to poke at the thing on the doorstep with sharp objects and blunt, to make us laugh in the middle of this endless year. Ladies and gentlemen I present to you the TOP TEN COMEDY VIDEOS ON YOUTUBE FOR AND ABOUT 2020. (Plus Ten More.) 

Obviously this is my opinion. Feel free to disagree. (And I know you will.) Do you any know videos I've overlooked (according to the rules!). (Watch the video!) Then please tell us all what they were in the comment section. But NO LINKS. YOUTUBE THINKS LINKS ARE SPAM. Just the title and the channel. (If you are confused about that just reread it again.)
